      "text": "reqs (fn & non fn)\ncore entities\nAPI / interface\nhigh level => fn\ndeep dives => complex setups : non fn",
      "fontSize": 20.016145833333333,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "reqs (fn & non fn)\ncore entities\nAPI / interface\nhigh level => fn\ndeep dives => complex setups : non fn",
