    {
      "id": "v1iboDJr1YYyPUmnvjYD4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 416.45703125,
      "y": -251.39453125,
      "width": 688.03955078125,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9m",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 463993440,
      "version": 495,
      "versionNonce": 2098211424,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771736013230,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Google docs\nconcurrent users on 1 doc? yes\nwant to show users position on the doc? yes\n\ncomments? no\nimages? no\n\nhow many concurrent users? 100\nhow many docs are we storing & how often are ppl creating this docs?\n1 billion docs, not too often\n100 million DAU\niamges? focus on text\nlatency for concurrent edits? roughly immediate?\n\navail >> consistency\nbut eventual consistent across users",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Google docs\nconcurrent users on 1 doc? yes\nwant to show users position on the doc? yes\n\ncomments? no\nimages? no\n\nhow many concurrent users? 100\nhow many docs are we storing & how often are ppl creating this docs?\n1 billion docs, not too often\n100 million DAU\niamges? focus on text\nlatency for concurrent edits? roughly immediate?\n\navail >> consistency\nbut eventual consistent across users",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "owlc-pep5KGLyIZULtw5j",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 408.05871749081905,
      "y": 169.98586856973515,
      "width": 503.0596923828125,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9n",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 481310304,
      "version": 397,
      "versionNonce": 157506464,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771736021980,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FUNC:\n- create a doc\n- write edits to doc\n- recv edits from doc\n- need user pos on doc\n\nNON FUNC:\n- handle 100 million DAU (WS => read/ write) [QPS]\n- handle 1 billion docs in storage [MEM]\n- latency (<500ms) for edits to be shown \n- availability >> consistency\n- eventual consistency of docs",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FUNC:\n- create a doc\n- write edits to doc\n- recv edits from doc\n- need user pos on doc\n\nNON FUNC:\n- handle 100 million DAU (WS => read/ write) [QPS]\n- handle 1 billion docs in storage [MEM]\n- latency (<500ms) for edits to be shown \n- availability >> consistency\n- eventual consistency of docs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
